    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Laurie Tunnicliffe</b>\n</p><p><b>Laurie Tunnicliffe</b>,<br />\nan Australian electronics engineer, as computer chess programmer author of the didactic <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess program</a> <a href=\"/LTChess\" title=\"LTChess\">LTChess</a>, written in <a href=\"/Pascal\" title=\"Pascal\">Pascal</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2013_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurie_Tunnicliffe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013_...\">2013 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurie_Tunnicliffe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2013 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=2491\">New open source chess program</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">lauriet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, November 03, 2013 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49972\">New Chess Program in Pascal</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 07, 2013 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51578\">Null move and LMR</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 12, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurie_Tunnicliffe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58527\">Null Move in Quiescent search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 09, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a> </li></ul>\n<p><b>2016</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60023\">How to speed up my engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 02, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60262\">Asymmetrical evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 24, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Asymmetric_Evaluation\" title=\"Asymmetric Evaluation\">Asymmetric Evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/Odd-Even_Effect\" title=\"Odd-Even Effect\">Odd-Even Effect</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60581\">Search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 24, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60790\">How to speed up my engine Part 2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 12, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60858\">Speed up your engine Part 3</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 18, 2016 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61020\">speed up your engine part 4</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 03, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Generation#Staged\" title=\"Move Generation\">Staged move generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61086\">Null Move in LMR</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 10, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">LMR</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61358\">Root search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 08, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">Root</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61792\">Max moves in a position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess#Maxima\" title=\"Chess\">Chess Maxima</a>, <a href=\"/Move_List\" title=\"Move List\">Move List</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62153\">Define end game</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 16, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame\" title=\"Endgame\">Endgame</a>, <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2017 ...</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64266\">End game and Null move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 12, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=65903\">TT in Qsearch</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 05, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67118\">Wiki</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurie Tunnicliffe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 15, 2018</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurie_Tunnicliffe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/laurie-tunnicliffe-4a7ba047/\">Laurie Tunnicliffe | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ltchess.weebly.com/\">LTChess - Home</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurie_Tunnicliffe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ltchess.weebly.com/\">LTChess - Home</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301094635\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 37/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 74/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/20